{"tid":1054292,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"場已卜，世清入一入嚟！","createTime":"2019-03-09T17:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T12:38:41.000Z","uid":60658,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"73e09b565ebb7423c599b56faf229e3dac5d1b3a","tid":1054292,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DkrRe9p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkrRe9p.png&h=68a3f272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卜場基本上無得揀 你我大家將就吓<br />\n觀塘瑞和街體育館 3月12日(星期日) 夜晚9點開始<br />\n<br />\n搵左個朋友(非連登仔)幫手做裁判<br />\n<br />\n規矩簡單少少<br />\n<br />\n1.打頭留力，禁插眼、撩陰<br />\n<br />\n2.戴唔戴護甲、拳套、頭盔自已揀<br />\n<br />\n.....可以再傾<br />\n<br />\n你有勇氣應約，我尊敬你，比面你 喊一聲世清，<br />\n<br />\n但如果你到時放我飛機，宇某可以負責任擔保，你不會有好結果！"},{"pid":"384687fb6a5e940689381a63358f123dcf523062","tid":1054292,"uid":60658,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"就快兩周年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f11dfabe100cff9be18e9648e244a9604b11ed","tid":1054292,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:21:49.000Z","msg":"樓主又笑世清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6e450ac98fe24abcaf414755ef7df912339503","tid":1054292,"uid":13874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:22:46.000Z","msg":"世清其實去左邊"},{"pid":"c9cd596531542df870a759d8a1ab6261f95485f3","tid":1054292,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"世清唔敢入"},{"pid":"95446ecafcf1456a9778bbb7ede5dc697b94397a","tid":1054292,"uid":60658,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be6e450ac98fe24abcaf414755ef7df912339503","tid":1054292,"ui